flow:

Client
 → Controller
   → Service
     → Repository
       → Database

Controller layer: Controller handles HTTP requests and responses
    Accept request
    Return response
    No business logic

Service Layer: container business logic
    Business logic
    validation
    Transacion handling

Repository Layer: Database interactino

DTO Vs Entity ?
  Entity - is for DB mapping
  DTO - is for API data transfer
so DTO prevents exposing internal entity structure!


